id":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4bcbe069572526e0a6a5cb2258f8245a2272fb","tid":1865934,"uid":95097,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"p95得唔得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"75c668cfcf3143bf06034af452c3490bb8ec2f91","tid":1865934,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21ac042ec4dabdeebc666872a78f51d2cfd0b946","tid":1865934,"uid":77966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"琴日上3m website 研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/1794572O/surgical-n95-vs-standard-n95-which-to-consider.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmultimedia.3m.com%2Fmws%2Fmedia%2F1794572O%2Fsurgical-n95-vs-standard-n95-which-to-consider.pdf&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAstTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=d3fc12ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/1794572O/surgical-n95-vs-standard-n95-which-to-consider.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nComparing Standard N95s to Surgical N95s<br />\nPutting this all together will help you differentiate between a standard NIOSH-certified N95 respirator and a surgical N95 respirator. While similar in appearance, the key difference is the fluid resistance and the resulting FDA clearance of surgical N95s. But when is that fluid resistance necessary?<br />\n<br />\nMany tasks performed by healthcare workers &ndash; such as patient intake and non-emergency patient evaluation &ndash; pose little to no risk of generating high-pressure streams of liquid and are not conducted in a sterile field. For workers performing such tasks, a primary potential hazard to consider is airborne viruses and bacteria, such as those generated by coughs and sneezes, which are effectively filtered by an N95 respirator.<br />\n<br />\nTherefore, if a healthcare facility is prioritizing respirator use &ndash; due to, for example, limited supply during a health emergency &ndash; they may want to consider prioritizing use of surgical N95 respirators for those healthcare workers requiring respiratory protection while performing surgery or other tasks that may expose them to high pressure streams of bodily fluid or conducting work in a sterile field. <strong>For other workers who will not be performing such surgical procedures or do not need to maintain a sterile field, a standard non-surgical N95 (or equivalent) respirator can be worn to help reduce those workers&rsquo; exposure to patient-generated airborne viruses and bacteria.</strong>"},{"pid":"6107670f860357f5480c8014c61ae33bc9d88104","tid":1865934,"uid":240973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73b92774c78950c958a1e11de8529c8acdedff7e","tid":1865934,"uid":2613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"之前啲連登仔日日喺度話工業用工業用<br />\n啲垃圾傳媒點樣報，佢哋就點樣信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37258ed478d7af2596e07c215414866e25ea0d1b","tid":1865934,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"on9以為地盤佬唔使接觸液體"},{"pid":"bdde812b907229c9b351ee5b0d7b5fa2fc0685cb","tid":1865934,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"9010得唔得？"},{"pid":"223428309de2e129f806f1dc71e7fea42895cd81","tid":1865934,"uid":151248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c668cfcf3143bf06034af452c3490bb8ec2f91","tid":1865934,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n有兩盒"},{"pid":"7f681dc899a69aedbfb55aaf4a1fc8c72a5ccc68","tid":1865934,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":